Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.21,0:01:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前吃壞肚子\N差點死掉的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師就是給我吃這個藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.92,0:02:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在送老師下山看醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.25,0:02:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會來不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.89,0:02:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就拿這藥和老師的命賭一賭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.43,0:02:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看能不能起死回生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.93,0:02:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十四話\N正邪對陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我左之助有多聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.14,0:02:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其自己胡亂尋找劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.11,0:02:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒不如靠警察的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.61,0:02:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上可以找到劍心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.62,0:02:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然看你們警察不順眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.02,0:02:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有時候倒還滿管用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.40,0:02:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們認識嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不很認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.97,0:02:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.17,0:02:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人很會製造麻煩\N所以把他關在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂  快放我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.01,0:02:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然我要自己開門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.32,0:03:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.19,0:03:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你們逼我這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.02,0:03:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.03,0:03:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,署長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙交給我就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您先上樓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.27,0:03:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想問你的事有很多件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.07,0:03:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要先問你\N東京的決鬥結果如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.11,0:03:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是大力士左之助\N力量這麼驚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.71,0:03:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你知道打架除了靠力氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要靠點腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道要怎樣防禦敵人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.72,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道你在胡說八道什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.89,0:03:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我左之助打架用自己的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.43,0:03:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠的是拳頭  不必靠什麼防禦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是孺子不可教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.47,0:04:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很忙  沒空在這和你耗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.21,0:04:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你是承認敗給我左之助了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨你怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是那麼看不起我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來啊  來打我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那間是關誰的牢房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.93,0:04:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來銅牆鐵壁似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.60,0:04:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那裏關的是頭號犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是緋村劍心抓來的張十刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半夜三更外頭在搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在吵什麼吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.18,0:04:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們安靜一點  我要睡覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有話問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.15,0:04:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.15,0:04:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前幾天神戶發生意外事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我派了五十個警察執勤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個晚上全被滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事情只有一個人做得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.73,0:05:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是志志雄那傢伙\N派人幹的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.23,0:05:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為我張十刀\N是你可以隨便吆喝的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你正經回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.48,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是正經回答你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.65,0:05:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你老實回答我\N或許我可以考慮把你放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會像別人那麼好騙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是志志雄的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.59,0:05:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好你被放了以後\N志志雄反而找人殺你滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.13,0:05:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你在這裏  反而安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.37,0:05:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個呆頭鵝的傢伙\N你以為我和你一樣無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.87,0:05:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏盡說些無聊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.64,0:05:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無聊  我最討厭人家說我無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.39,0:06:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來打啊  你這個掃把星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求之不得  你這個呆頭雞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掃把星  呆頭雞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.43,0:06:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掃把星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.43,0:06:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掃把星  呆頭雞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.83,0:06:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你贏我\N我就回答你的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就叫那個人做裁判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們拼看看誰會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們開始打吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.19,0:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不巧   打中頭蓋骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.43,0:06:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用拳頭打架算是男子漢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.74,0:06:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你需要我幫你解開腳鐐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.91,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我如果繼續和你打\N倒霉的會是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.25,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼問題快問吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.89,0:07:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就快說吧\N我剛才問你的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.83,0:07:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果被這傢伙利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我究竟是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.70,0:07:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在一、二小時間殺光\N精銳部隊五十人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是志志雄的二個部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有二人  真沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.67,0:07:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有時間限制\N我也可以殺五十個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.01,0:07:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有這麼厲害  真看不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.19,0:07:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你是志志雄部下中\N武功最差的一個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個笨蛋胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還沒有回答完我的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.67,0:07:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個是天劍宗次郎\N就是常常奸笑的那一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.77,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次就是宗次郎\N邀集江湖中的十大名刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來為志志雄效力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們差不多應該到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.43,0:08:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武林十大高手  終於要到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史上十大高手\N都來歸附志志雄先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.84,0:08:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安慈、蝙也也到了\N剩下的四個不久也會到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治先生  有刺客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.12,0:08:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛還在這兒的  怎麼不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.35,0:08:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏也沒有  跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.99,0:08:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰好大膽  敢來這兒攪亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.49,0:08:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起  請您再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.26,0:08:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安慈他們已經去收拾那刺客了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒這個必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.67,0:09:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒必要去收拾我們的同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收拾同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.41,0:09:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙已經來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的功力又增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你嗎  宇水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.06,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盲劍宇水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.66,0:09:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治維新前 在幕府擔任殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.77,0:09:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一次和志志雄拚鬥\N雙目被刺失明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.61,0:09:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來為了報仇  不斷修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終成劍術高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.18,0:09:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為江湖中數一數二\N眼盲心不盲的盲劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.49,0:09:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒什麼好氣的  我要殺你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是輕而易舉的事\N只是看我的心情好壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.83,0:10:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄就是看上我這一點的\N不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.83,0:10:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說的是  你幹嘛裝作刺客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.77,0:10:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進來殺死這些士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.97,0:10:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千人軍隊我都不看在眼裏\N何況只是這些無名小卒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.58,0:10:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來這兒的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.78,0:10:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在神戶那兒已經\N殺了五十個警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你總是這麼沉不住氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇水  你來這裏途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.22,0:10:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有遇見左臉有十字傷疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.33,0:10:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和身材高大叫做齊藤的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.93,0:10:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.27,0:10:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我們最大的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎  這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你和他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.91,0:10:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們三個就是我最大的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天劍宗次郎和盲劍宇水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是志志雄手下最強的二個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.65,0:11:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的武功或許不錯\N但宇水比你更強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.92,0:11:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙很得意的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再問你一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.96,0:11:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛剛收到一個情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.03,0:11:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備毀滅京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.41,0:11:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毀滅京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.38,0:11:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我\N志志雄準備怎樣毀滅京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 看來只好老實告訴你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.20,0:11:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道池田屋事件嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.08,0:11:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽過而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在京都池田屋旅館裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.59,0:12:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維新激進分子\N在那計劃暗殺政府高官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.23,0:12:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並襲擊新撰組成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.07,0:12:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時計劃派兵五百人火燒京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.10,0:12:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要將京都燒為平地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.17,0:12:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時燒光所有的政府官員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.78,0:12:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄就是要模仿這個事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.78,0:12:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不同的是\N維新分子是暗地裏進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.42,0:12:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄卻是光明正大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向敵人宣戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.30,0:12:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等江湖十大高手全員到齊後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.60,0:12:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即可展開戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.61,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都在日本人心中\N是不朽的千年王城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是根深蒂固的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦京都被毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.22,0:13:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人民對政府的信賴\N也就會消失殆盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.09,0:13:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒掉京都對政府還不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可憐的是那裏的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從幕府動亂到現在已經十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.33,0:13:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時局好不容易\N才開始平穩下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.87,0:13:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再也禁不起任何一點的破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.78,0:13:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我左之助絕對不能讓京都毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.19,0:13:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我身為新撰組的隊長\N絕對要阻止這場浩劫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.03,0:13:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.93,0:13:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你想辦法都是用這種方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.87,0:14:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你決鬥等下次吧\N先讓我出去找劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.34,0:14:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你這種笨蛋決鬥\N只是浪費時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你如果要找劍心  就快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.91,0:14:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在這囉囉嗦嗦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.88,0:14:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要命令我\N我又不是你的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你想一直待在這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想把我和這傢伙關在一起嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.69,0:14:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還不快出來 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.96,0:14:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.72,0:14:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.67,0:14:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了  臉色那麼難看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去哪裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.17,0:14:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天待在這裏都快悶死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.01,0:14:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易出去買了這盒點心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.31,0:14:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,買這要花三天時間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外面太好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不在的時候\N宇水那奇怪的傢伙來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說宇水怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇水  好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,近來可好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.13,0:15:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實你出去都是有任務的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.80,0:15:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的眼睛雖瞎心裏卻明白得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.21,0:15:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使像你這種冷酷無情的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.05,0:15:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也逃不過我的心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.11,0:15:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.55,0:15:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正你們在做什麼\N完全與我無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我差點忘記告訴你們\N剩下的三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.03,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天會來報到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鐮足先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.34,0:15:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了  宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一次終於可以一決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.28,0:15:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看誰可以得到志志雄的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.35,0:15:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不會輸給你這個男人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,娘娘腔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些年輕人真有活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才槌老人  你看來也很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你對我這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些年輕警衛別說敬老尊賢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.57,0:16:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到我也不向我打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.11,0:16:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是在嫉妒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.58,0:16:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.11,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.15,0:16:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有人不讓我進來這兒哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了  全部都到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起  志志雄先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我離開了三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是給您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等會再告訴我你去玩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.71,0:16:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝  待會再吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.25,0:17:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能臨時有事\N張十刀沒有準時報到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.06,0:17:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等他來了\N十位江湖高手就都齊聚一堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.76,0:17:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論是愛我的\N或是想殺我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是對明治政府失望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.23,0:17:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我們各有各的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我相信\N只要集結我們的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.27,0:17:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對可以打贏這場仗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.38,0:17:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蝙也  夷腕坊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美  方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐮足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有宇水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.22,0:17:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於要開始我們的佔領計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明晚十一時五十九分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.76,0:17:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始火燒京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.57,0:17:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將京都燒個片甲不留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.22,0:18:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼還在這裏睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.23,0:18:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家不是都在等你回去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在這幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕快下山去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.91,0:18:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不習慣被男人抱著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了  這個藥果然有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.36,0:18:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個藥有效\N這個藥只是我隨便調的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.26,0:18:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.13,0:18:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是這把刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這把逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.64,0:19:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看  這把刀的目釘脫落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.11,0:19:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吸收了你的劍力\N因而將力道減到最低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.05,0:19:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是一把善解人意的好刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.82,0:19:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤空的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.39,0:19:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我一向自以為豪的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.99,0:19:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍與人合而為一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.19,0:19:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然你還沒完全熟練技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.40,0:19:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但「天翔龍閃」你已學成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.30,0:19:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在最重要的是\N要將「天翔龍閃」完全熟練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.87,0:19:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人劍合一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.55,0:19:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師  你保重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你收下這個白斗篷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.33,0:20:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是飛天御劍流\N繼承者的資格證物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得  這並不適合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.84,0:20:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我已學會飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.64,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我並不想承襲您的名氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要的只是飛天御劍的真理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.75,0:20:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是你一個人所能決定的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.66,0:20:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你向來就是這樣  我行我素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便你怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.67,0:20:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師能不能幫我保護\N葵屋裏的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.71,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要太得寸進尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你如果不願繼承飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.48,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就還是我的徒弟\N我也就是你的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.49,0:21:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不是為了你個人的私利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.06,0:21:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才教你飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要記住這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.07,0:21:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心不該擔心的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去打敗志志雄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上巡邏的警察特別多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.07,0:21:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藤田  藤田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天助我也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.01,0:21:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.81,0:21:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今早出現在山麓駐紮處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.65,0:22:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正飛車趕來我們這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.95,0:22:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就會抵達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.12,0:22:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.88,0:22:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.88,0:22:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已不是以前的緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.42,0:22:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼短的時間\N他究竟做了什麼

